## üß† Why MetaForge?

Most libraries focus only on one type of solver. MetaForge unifies traditional, bio-inspired, and learning-based approaches in one clean, extensible Python package ‚Äî built for experimentation, benchmarking, and educational use.

Whether you're doing a thesis, publishing research, or solving real-world factory problems ‚Äî **MetaForge is your launchpad**. üöÄ

